      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">52.209-2</ph> Prohibition on Contracting with Inverted Domestic Corporations-Representation.</title>
      <conbody outputclass="provision" class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d3122e8" class="- topic/p ">As prescribed in <ph outputclass="ClauseProvisionXREF" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="9.108-5.dita#FAR_9_108_5"
                     base="i1116431"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">9.108-5</xref>(a)</ph>, insert the following provision:</p>
         <p outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps" class="- topic/p " id="d3122e15">Prohibition on Contracting with Inverted Domestic Corporations-Representation <ph outputclass="SmCaps" class="- topic/ph ">(Nov 2015)</ph>
         </p>
         <ol id="d3089e25" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3122e21" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Definitions</i>. "Inverted domestic corporation" and "subsidiary" have the meaning given in the clause of this contract entitled Prohibition on Contracting with Inverted Domestic Corporations (<xref href="52.209-10.dita#FAR_52_209_10"
                        base="i1062680"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.209-10</xref>).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3122e31" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            Government agencies are not permitted to use appropriated (or otherwise made available) funds for contracts with either an inverted domestic corporation, or a subsidiary of an inverted domestic corporation, unless the exception at <xref href="9.108-2.dita#FAR_9_108_2"
                        base="i1116407"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">9.108-2</xref>(b) applies or the requirement is waived in accordance with the procedures at <xref href="9.108-4.dita#FAR_9_108_4"
                        base="i1116422"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">9.108-4</xref>.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3122e42" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Representation</i>. The Offeror represents that-</p>
               <ol id="d3089e68" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3122e50" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
								                It <cite outputclass="Checkbox" xtrc="52.209-2_d49e52" class="- topic/cite ">□</cite> is, <cite outputclass="Checkbox" xtrc="52.209-2_d49e55" class="- topic/cite ">□</cite> is not an inverted domestic corporation; and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3122e61" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
								                It <cite outputclass="Checkbox" xtrc="52.209-2_d49e63" class="- topic/cite ">□</cite> is, <cite outputclass="Checkbox" xtrc="52.209-2_d49e66" class="- topic/cite ">□</cite> is not a subsidiary of an inverted domestic corporation.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
         </ol>
         <p outputclass="Endofprovision" class="- topic/p ">(End of provision)</p>
